assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Tierra Properties S.C Ltd produces, sells, and markets food ingredients in Israel and internationally. The company offers legumes and grains, vegetables, tomato products, and orchard and tropical fruits, as well as Mediterranean fruits comprising lemons, oranges, grapefruits, limes, prickly pears, olives, and avocados in the aseptic food, freeze dried, and spray dried food product lines. It provides tomato powder, lemon powder, and vegetable bleaches, as well as non-dairy thickeners/whiteners; products that are pasteurized and packaged in aseptic packaging, including tomato, diced red bell pepper, and chickpeas-based products, as well as various sauces; organic tomato paste; roasted and peeled bell peppers; roasted eggplant puree; and freeze-drying food and nutritional supplements comprising citrus and avocado powder, sweet potato precooked, and red quinoa precooked. The company also sells products and provides services in the process of drying using freeze-drying technology; provides tomato processing services for aseptic tomato products; dries and sells a range of legumes, grains, and citrus products as a raw material for the food industry; and develops and sells ready-made meals. It serves food companies and institutional markets. The company sells its products through warehouses and distributors. The company was formerly known as Cham Foods (Israel) Ltd. The company was incorporated in 1970 and is based in Tel Aviv-Yafo, Israel. Tierra Properties S.C Ltd is a subsidiary of M. Shvi Family's Asset Ltd.
